climate

Class ClimateRecordList

  • java.lang.Object
    • climate.ClimateRecordList

  • public class ClimateRecordList
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores a list of all the climate records that share the same date. It can then calculate the mean temps and mean precip of all these records and store it in a bucket.
    Author:
    Marcus Lorenzana
